  ('dietitian-moex-07081', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在有絲分裂（mitosis）過程中DNA發生損傷時，磷酸化的p53蛋白會抑制細胞繼續進行有絲分裂，直到 損傷DNA被修復。若受損的DNA一直都沒有被修復，細胞將會發生下列何種情況？ 細胞重返至G1期（G1 phase）  細胞重複進行S期（S phase） 細胞重複進行G2期（G2 phase）  細胞凋亡（apoptosis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07082', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在細胞凋亡（apoptosis）過程中，蛋白質水解（proteolysis）是由下列何種物質所負責？ ubiquitin    autophagic lysosomal protease phagocytic protease    caspase', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "387d240e6a2b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3812a09b1c9a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "106", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
